-Oi!

521
00:39:43.757 --> 00:39:46.093
It's good to see
you smiling again.

522
00:39:49.930 --> 00:39:51.348
Yeah. I miss him.

523
00:39:51.431 --> 00:39:54.267
Course you do. You always will.

524
00:39:55.435 --> 00:39:58.563
-What if I never meet anyone like him?
-You won't.

525
00:39:59.397 --> 00:40:01.942
